      "id": 21,
      "options": {
        "content": "### What the dashboard is telling you\n\n**Estimated spend** is cc-blackbox's best local cost estimate. Use it for trends; it may not match your bill exactly.\n\n**Finished sessions** are sessions cc-blackbox has closed and saved a final diagnosis for.\n\n**Problem sessions** are finished sessions where cc-blackbox found a real problem, such as repeated tool failures, cache rebuilds, or a model switch.\n\n**Cache reused** means Claude could reuse cached input instead of writing that context again. Higher usually means faster and cheaper sessions.\n\n**Cache expired misses** happen when cached context aged out before the next turn, so it had to be rebuilt.\n\n**Fast rebuild misses** happen when the cache is rebuilt again soon after a previous rebuild. That often means the prompt or setup is changing too much.\n\n**Model switches** mean the model that answered was different from the model requested.\n\n**Tool failures** are tool results that came back as errors.",
        "mode": "markdown"
      },
      "pluginVersion": "11.1.0",
      "title": "How to read this dashboard",
      "description": "Plain-English definitions for the numbers on this dashboard.",
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
